Package edu.odu.cs.cs350

Class HTMLDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.odu.cs.cs350.HTMLDocument
  • public class HTMLDocument
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates an object that contains the lists of all the different extracted content: scrips, stylesheets, images, and anchors.
